  <summary date="2022-12-21T20:17:33Z" status="Reported to Senate">READ Act Reauthorization Act of 2022

This bill reauthorizes a law that requires the implementation of a strategy to promote quality basic education in partner countries by (1) expanding access to basic education for all children, particularly marginalized children and vulnerable groups; and (2) improving the quality of basic education and learning outcomes.</summary>
